oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ray Whitley Program - 1969-08-01 Programs: I-VIII
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Ray Whitley (musician/entertainer) and his Six-Bar Cowboys (musical group) performances for multiple entertainment pieces. The recordings feature: Redskin and Redhead, California or Bust, Corraling a School Marm, Musical Bandit, Ranch House Romeo, and Prairie Papa. The tape was gathered on August 01, 1969. Tape is labeled as reel one, programs I-VIII.
